B.Hk=s(["{#}Architected and developed a high-performance Segmentation Engine from scratch using Go-lang and Java, enabling the Growth team to execute precise, data-driven user targeting.","{#}Designed real-time data pipelines leveraging Apache Flink and Kafka for stream processing, integrated with Apache Druid for high-concurrency analytical queries.","{#}Authored comprehensive RFCs (Request for Comments) and led technical research to establish the foundational architecture for the segmentation ecosystem.","{#}Pioneered research on Anonymous Data Production for UAT environments, implementing a Data Lakehouse architecture using Trino, Parquet, and cross-cloud integration (GCP &amp; AWS)","{#}Developed automated data-provisioning tools to deliver high-quality raw datasets to the Data Science team for advanced behavioral analysis.","{#}Ensured data privacy and security by managing complex data masking and transformation workflows between production and development environments."],t.s)
