B.Iv=s(["Developed and optimized the Qurban distribution engine for Kitabisa\u2019s web and mobile platforms, streamlining the end-to-end digital procurement and distribution process.","{#}Core Feature Development: Engineered robust modules for qurban livestock purchasing, scheduling, and information dissemination systems.","{#}Progress Tracking System: Implemented a real-time tracking feature to provide donors with transparent updates on the slaughtering and distribution stages.","{#}System Reliability: Leveraged Go-Lang and Microservices architecture to ensure high availability and performance during peak seasonal traffic."],t.s)
