B.I6=s(["Working on POS (Point of Sales) & PPOB (Payment Point Online Banking) projects, utilizing an offline-first architecture with real-time operations powered by Firebase Firestore.","Initiated and conducted independent research and a Proof of Concept (POC) to resolve critical performance bottlenecks regarding Flutter's real-time data handling, which was subsequently validated and approved by the CTO.","Led the full-scale migration from Flutter to Android Native (Java), successfully overseeing the entire implementation process from architecture design to production deployment."],t.s)
